hiveArticle.title: B&W Photo Contest - Travel - Entry #1 - Dubai Trip
hiveArticle.body:
This is my first entry for the B&W photo contest initiated by @daveks and judged by @exploretraveler.

### Dubai Trip

I had visited Dubai in the month of February for 4 days. It was a pleasant stay, and I must admit that there are a lot of places to visit. The below image was taken from the Palm Monorail which runs along the trunk of the Palm Jumeirah in Dubai.

<hr>

  ![image](https://img.esteem.ws/ua3mecgv0x.jpg)

<hr>

Camera : Motorola X Play, Edited to Black and White
